<title>NIGERIA: Nigerian Afprint full year profit rises.</title>
<headline>Nigerian Afprint full year profit rises.</headline>
<dateline>LAGOS 1997-07-04</dateline>
<text>
<p>Full year result for Nigerian textile group Afprint to end-March 1997. (In million naira unless stated).</p>
<p>				  1997	   1996</p>
<p>Turnover			5,800 vs 6,900</p>
<p>Profit before taxation    359.7 vs 217.5</p>
<p>Taxation			 16.4 vs 17.3</p>
<p>Profit after taxation     343.3 vs 200.2</p>
<p>Dividend per share	30 kobo vs 20 kobo</p>
<p>($1=84.5 naira)</p>
<p>-- Lagos newsroom +234 1 263 03 17</p>
</text>
